<i>Things work out right</i>

1353
01:51:16,192 --> 01:51:19,569
<i>Go by</i>

1354
01:51:21,697 --> 01:51:24,074
<i>Things on my mind</i>

1355
01:51:24,242 --> 01:51:26,701
<i>And I just don't have the time</i>

1356
01:51:26,869 --> 01:51:30,330
<i>And it don't seem right</i>

1357
01:51:33,085 --> 01:51:35,168
<i>Ain't seen a day</i>

1358
01:51:35,337 --> 01:51:38,131
<i>That I don't hear people say</i>

1359
01:51:38,299 --> 01:51:41,384
<i>They know they're gonna die</i>

1360
01:51:44,430 --> 01:51:47,307
<i>This may seem a little bit crazy</i>

1361
01:51:47,476 --> 01:51:51,687
<i>But I don't think you
should be so lazy</i>

1362
01:51:55,694 --> 01:51:58,153
<i>If you think
you've heard this before</i>

1363
01:51:58,320 --> 01:52:00,156
<i>Well, stick around</i>

1364
01:52:00,322 --> 01:52:04,033
<i>I'm gonna tell you more</i>

1365
01:53:30,629 --> 01:53:33,464
<i>One just like the other</i>

1366
01:53:33,631 --> 01:53:35,592
<i>Sin's a good man's brother</i>

1367
01:53:35,759 --> 01:53:39,471
<i>But is that right?</i>

1368
01:53:41,890 --> 01:53:44,393
<i>You tell me that I don't</i>

1369
01:53:44,560 --> 01:53:46,769
<i>Then I say I won't</i>

1370
01:53:46,938 --> 01:53:50,691
<i>But then I might</i>

1371
01:53:53,403 --> 01:53:56,114
<i>You said this is the way
it's supposed to be<i>

1372
01:53:56,281 --> 01:53:58,783
<i>But it just don't seem
right to me</i>

1373
01:53:58,951 --> 01:54:02,912
<i>And that's outta sight</i>

1374
01:54:04,498 --> 01:54:07,418
<i>Some folks need an education</i>

1375
01:54:07,585 --> 01:54:11,964
<i>Don't give up
or we'll lose the nation</i>

1376
